# Nix conventions — ticketing

Dense overview: `AGENTS.md`, module map `modules/README.md`, cross-cutting `.vibe/docs/architecture.md`.

## Module shape
- Standard args: `{ config, lib, pkgs, ... }` — use `with lib;` where the rest of the file already does
- Bind config: `let cfg = config.zugvoegel.services.<name>; in …`
- Expose `options.zugvoegel.services.<name>` and gate system config with `config = mkIf cfg.enable { … };`

## Options
- Prefer `mkEnableOption`, `mkOption` with `types.*` from `lib.types`
- Match naming, style, and option structure of neighboring modules (e.g. `modules/pretix`, `modules/schwarmplaner`)

## Validate locally
- `nixos-rebuild build --flake '.#pretix-server-01'`

## Cross-cutting
- Backups, nginx, Docker stacks: follow patterns in sibling module READMEs and `.vibe/docs/design.md`
